
Pig Farm

Overview: "Our pig farm is dedicated to raising healthy and happy pigs using sustainable and humane practices. We breed and raise a variety of pig species, including pure-line large white and pure-line land race. We offer high-quality pork products to our customers."

Fish Section

Overview: "Our fish section is a state-of-the-art aquaculture facility where we raise a variety of fish including catfish. We use advanced water management systems and sustainable feeding practices to ensure the health and well-being of our fish."

Fish Feed Production Unit

Overview: "Our fish feed production unit manufactures high-quality feed for our fish and other aquatic animals. We use a combination of natural ingredients and advanced manufacturing techniques to produce feed that is nutritious and sustainable."


Goat Section

Overview: "Our goat section is home to a diverse herd of goats, including dairy and meat breeds. We offer high-quality goat milk and dairy products, as well as goat meat and other products."

Sheep Section

Overview: "Our sheep section is dedicated to raising healthy and productive sheep using sustainable and humane practices. We offer high-quality lamb meat products."

Grasscutter Section

Overview: "Our grasscutter section is focused on breeding and raising high-quality grasscutters for meat and other products. We use sustainable and humane practices to ensure the health and well-being of our animals."

Poultry Section

Overview: "Our poultry section is home to a variety of bird species, including chickens, turkeys, and ducks. We offer high-quality eggs, meat, and other poultry products, as well as breeding and hatchery services."
