Overview: "Our snail section is a pioneering venture in snail farming, dedicated to breeding and raising high-quality snails for both domestic and international markets. We use state-of-the-art facilities and sustainable practices to ensure the health and well-being of our snails, and offer a range of products including fresh snails an snail meat. Our snail farm is designed to meet the highest standards of hygiene and food safety, and we are committed to providing our customers with the freshest and highest-quality snails possible."





    
